com.hpl.mds.annotations.processor.parser

Class SchemaParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hpl.mds.annotations.processor.parser.SchemaParser

  • public class SchemaParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Parser for the schema's content including fields, instance, static and abstract methods and constructors. The parsed information is retrieved in the form of a RecordInfo
    Author:
    Abraham Alcantara
